<br>
This isn't necessarily true. Some people (like myself) solo if they know they will only be on for a short while, or will have to go afk a lot while they are on. <br>
<br>
Its actually more a matter of being considerate to guild/group mates that I not seek out a group in those situations. <br>
<br>
Nerfing solo xp would be silly at this point in the game. It would make it too difficult to level up a new toon if you ever decided to do it, and absolutely destroy the game for people that can't log in for more than an hour at a time.<br>
<br>
At the same time, it would make things more difficult for people who do group all the time, as you'd see more people in my situation having to get into groups for short periods of time, causing more downtime for existing groups when we decide to leave.<br>
<br>
Realistically, it would be nice to see a group xp bonus, but maybe consider adding it to the Non-PoP zones. Group XP seems to be moving adequately up in the planes. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=381929"> Naladini </a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
