- make grouping exp better/nerf solo exp. make mobs hit even harder than they do currently, and have them give a little more exp. add a 7th slot to groups (to account for the influx of players who formerly were soloing).<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
The only thing that needs to happen is for group experience to get way better.  My personal opinion is that you should get the same amount of experience for killing something grouped as you do solo.  The experience shouldn't be split.  The group bonus is what the bonus for grouping should be.  Right now Verant believes that the bonus is that you can kill faster plus the xp bonus.  I don't think the fact that you can kill faster makes a big enough difference when factored with splitting the xp. Groups should also be 8 persons big.  I think DAoC did this portion of the game the right way.<br>
