<br>
I think people truly take most of the mage summons for granted.  Mod Rods are a easy 7mana per tick regen that stacks with everything for the casters in your group. The ability to summon focus items for members of your groups is a great ability to have. Our summoned pet goods are really great and not only improve our pets but help to improve the pets of our groupmates. CoTH while no longer glamorous still has many uses. It is a great pulling tool if you need to split mobs and there is no monk in your group. Mage + Ranger &gt; Monks for split pulling most areas. Damage shields are also very nice utility as well.  I am very happy with the state of our utility.<br>
